  "body": "## Description\r\nAdd tests to verify ChatGLM chat model's error handling for invalid API addresses and timeouts, covering sync, async, and streaming request modes.\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n- Ran `make format`, `make lint` and `make test` from the root of the `langchain` package, all checks passed (only minor type checker import warnings, no impact on test execution).\r\n- Manually executed the new test cases to confirm they correctly validate error behaviors of ChatGLM under invalid API/timeout scenarios.\r\n\r\n## Additional Notes\r\n- No breaking changes, no dependency modifications, and no updates to `uv.lock`/`pyproject.toml` files.\r\n- This PR only touches the `langchain` package (specifically test files under `chat_models`), adhering to single-package modification guidelines.\r\n",
